OL,3,CStudent left stranded by Belfast
OL,4,CGlider wins #7k discrimination payout
OL,6,FA student who uses an electric
OL,7,Fwheelchair has settled a disability
OL,8,Fdiscrimination case against public
OL,9,Ftransport provider Translink after she
OL,10,Fwas carried past her stop several
OL,11,Ftimes while travelling on the Glider
OL,12,Fbus service.
OL,14,FThe case brought by Rosie Pidgeon,
OL,15,Fsupported by the Equality Commission
OL,16,Ffor Northern Ireland, was settled for
OL,17,F#7,500 with no admission of liability.
