OL,3,CStudent left stranded by Belfast
OL,4,CGlider wins #7k discrimination payout
OL,6,FTranslink said it would implement
OL,7,Fchanges to ensure "sonsistency of
OL,8,Fservice" and provide "refresher"
OL,9,Ftraining to staff.
OL,11,FMiss Pidgeon said she regularly
OL,12,Ftravels on the Glider to and from her
OL,13,Fcollege course at Millfield campus in
OL,14,FBelfast.
OL,16,FShe said that to disembark, she needs
OL,17,Fto press a specific blue bell, while
OL,18,Fthe Glider is moving, to alert the
OL,19,Fdriver to lower the ramp at the next
OL,20,Fstop.
