OL,4,CGlider wins #7k discrimination payout
OL,6,FSince beginning her commute in 2022,
OL,7,FMiss Pidgeon said that on various
OL,8,Foccasions, drivers have failed to
OL,9,Fdeploy the ramp.
OL,11,FShe said she has been unable to signal
OL,12,Fto the driver that the ramp has failed
OL,13,Fto deploy as the bell does not ring
OL,14,Fonce the bus has stopped.
OL,16,FWithout the ramp, she is unable to
OL,17,Fdisembark and said she had been
OL,18,Fcarried on past her destination on
OL,19,Fsome occasions. She says she been left
OL,20,Fstranded at Dundonald Park and Ride
OL,21,Fwhere the Glider terminates.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
