OL,3,CStudent left stranded by Belfast
OL,4,CGlider wins #7k discrimination payout
OL,6,FMiss Pidgeon said: "I value my
OL,7,Findependence and just want to be able
OL,8,Fto travel to and from college without
OL,9,Fany worry or stress.
OL,11,F"Being carried past my stop is
OL,12,Fdistressing, and exhausting. It leaves
OL,13,Fme late for class or I arrive home
OL,14,Fcompletely dispirited.
OL,16,F"Due to my disability, which I
OL,17,Facquired as a result of Covid, it
OL,18,Ftakes a long time for me to recover
OL,19,Ffrom each incident."
