OL,6,FShe added: "I have raised complaints
OL,7,Fwith Translink and explained the toll
OL,8,Fit takes on me. They did carry out
OL,9,Finvestigations and previously
OL,10,Fapologised, but it continued to happen.
OL,12,F"I felt I had no choice but to pursue
OL,13,Fthis case. I want to make sure that
OL,14,Fall wheelchair users can use the
OL,15,FGlider with confidence."
