OL,6,FEoin O'Neill, director of legal
OL,7,Fservices at the Equality Commission
OL,8,Fsaid: "All transport providers in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland have duties under the
OL,10,FDisability Discrimination Act in
OL,11,Frelation to the provision and use of
OL,12,Fthe vehicles they provide.
OL,14,F"This includes making 'reasonable
OL,15,Fadjustments' to take away or overcome
OL,16,Felements in their services which
OL,17,Fpresent barriers to disabled people.
OL,19,F"The Glider has a system to alert the
OL,20,Fdriver to deploy the ramp.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
