OL,6,F"All drivers must be fully trained in
OL,7,Fensuring the ramp is deployed when
OL,8,Frequested and made aware of the
OL,9,Fpotential impact on their disabled
OL,10,Fpassenger if they fail to do so."
OL,12,FHe added: "Many people with
OL,13,Fdisabilities rely on public transport
OL,14,Fto go about their daily lives.
OL,16,F"They must be able to board at the
OL,17,Fstop of their choosing and disembark
OL,18,Fwhere they need to."
