OL,6,FIan Campbell, Translink's director of
OL,7,Fservice operations, said the company
OL,8,Fapologised for any hurt and distress
OL,9,Fcaused.
OL,11,FHe added: "We are dedicated to making
OL,12,Four services and facilities accessible
OL,13,Fand inclusive for everyone,
OL,14,Frecognising the importance of this in
OL,15,Fenabling more people to live
OL,16,Findependent and productive lives.
