OL,6,F"To better accommodate passengers who
OL,7,Fuse wheelchairs, we have introduced
OL,8,Fchanges to our procedures that will
OL,9,Fimprove the consistency of service
OL,10,Fprovided to our customers particularly
OL,11,Fwhen boarding and alighting Glider
OL,12,Fvehicles.
OL,14,F"Additionally, we have provided
OL,15,Frefresher training to further
OL,16,Fstrengthen our procedures.
OL,18,F"We will continue to invest in our
OL,19,Ffacilities, services and staff
OL,20,Ftraining as part of our ongoing
OL,21,Faccessibility programme.
